I developed and implemented test, operations and maintenance procedures and was the only flight test engineer on the program certified to write test work orders (impromptu, unique, system and component-level test procedures) for all defined engineering disciplines and systems. I also conducted airborne and ground tests, ensured test completion and aircrew and air vehicle safety, and directed preflight, postflight, launch and recovery operations. .
